---
title: Onion Chutney-Glazed Haloumi with Herby Roasted Veggies, Garlic Yoghurt & Lemon
description: An onion chutney is truly an all-rounder. It can go with anything, so why not try it with squeaky haloumi? It’s going to
blow your mind with the sweet and sticky tastes on top of roast veggie toss. It’s another win for onion chutney!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
